name: The Department of Wildlife and Fisheries
description: "The Department of Wildlife and Fisheries". Perfect hat for all outdoor activities. This hat is part nylon, part cotton, has three vent holes and a leather back latch strap. This is the first in our new series of Wildlife themed hats.

name: SC Athletics "NYC Division 1A"
description:
This is the 3rd design from our all new Athletics line SC13 Athletics. This design features an original illustration of a "ringsman"
on the front panel, along with the print "NYC Division 1A". SC13 Athletics is printed on the back as well.

name: SC Athletics Orange & Tan Mesh
description:
The second hat from our new Athletics line. This cotton and mesh hat has a 3d embroidery of SC, with Sun Cycle New
York City embroidered flat below it.

name: SCNYC 13 Pocket Hat
description: The SCNY13 nylon adjustable shortbill hat with front panel Velcro stash pocket. Limited Edition.

name: SC Athletics "Rings-man"
description:
This is the first design from our all new Athletics line SC13 Athletics. This design features an original illustration of a a
“rings-man” on the front panel and an additional SC Athletic print on the back. Also featuring an insert tab to tuck in
any extra length of the back strap.

name: SC Crest Short
description:
All new Nylon and cotton hat, with SC crest printed on the front panel. This is a adjustable short bill hat. Size S/M 

This design is also available in long bill.

name: Build Long Bill Hat
description:
"Build" Long Bill hat. Vintage inspired, attention to detail, and top notch craftsmanship makes this one of our most popular hats. Recently nicknamed the "13 Panel Hat" for its intricate stitching and panels. Its a 5 panel style hat, made up of 13 different panels. 
This hat is Olive Green. Same color as the short bill. Picture may appear darker than the hat is.

name: SC NYC-13 Long Bill
description: "SC NYC-13" Long Bill Hat. This is a vintage inspired Nylon hat. Made up of blue and red panels, with a yellow latch back. This hat has a comfortable fit. Its weather resistant, and perfect for sunny Spring activities.

name: The NYC Route Long Bill
description: This is our newest hat for Spring 2013. "The NYC Route" is a cotton Long bill 5 Panel Hat. This is a Army green and Tan hat, with black under brim. We added a brand new feature the "buckle back", tech snap in. For extra comfort and durability. These are a limited edition. Only 100 made, and going fast.

name: Nautical 93
description: "Nautical 93" This is our first polyester hat. The hat has three embroideries. The material allows for a light, comfortable fit. These hats are great for rainy days, or outdoor activities sailing, yachting, rafting, kayaking or just looking good.

name: SC NYC-13 Short Bill
description: "SC NYC-13" Short Bill Hat. This is a vintage inspired Nylon hat. Made up of blue and red panels, with a yellow latch back. This hat has a comfortable fit. Its weather resistant, and perfect for sunny Spring activities. This is a Limited Edition.

name: Ideology
description: "Ideology" 5 Panel Hat. This is our first collaboration with recording artist IDE of Creative Juices Music. The Ideology Logo printed on the front panel. This is a cotton hat with, a comfortable fit.

name: Ninety Five.2
description: The "Ninety Five.2" 5 panel hat is a cotton hat, made to match some of your favorite sneakers. This hat has "Ninety Five" embroidered on the back, a neon green under-brim, and extra lining for, comfort and durability.

name: USA Shield
description: Designed for a breathable, relaxed fit, and with a flexible bill, this 5 panel red, white & blue hat was quality manufactured with your comfort in mind. Details include USA Shield side logo, easy snap expandable back strap and an extra layer of insulation for durability.

name: 1988 Limited Edition
description: 1988 Limited Edition 5 panel red, white & blue hat with 1988 graphic on front and "NY/NJ" on back.

name: SC Athletics T Shirt
description: SC Athletics High quality T shirt, with no tag, and printed label. This design was created by Sue Works. These are limited Edition only 100 printed.
